𝗗𝗮𝘆 𝟯𝟴: 𝗙𝗼𝗰𝘂𝘀 𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗲𝗹𝗶𝘃𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗩𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗲!
💡 "In Scrum, value beats velocity every time!"  
👉 Tip: Don’t chase speed—chase value. Ensure the team is focused on delivering what’s most important to the customer.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
-----

🧠 Poll: "Does your team focus more on delivering value or velocity?"  
1. Always on value 💡  
2. Mostly on value 🎯  
3. A bit of both 📊  
4. Velocity is the focus 🚀
